title: Pleasantly surprised
text: This was my second order from Temu. The first order is scheduled to arrive today. The shipping has been within the timeframe given at the time of my order. I was kept updated via text as my package processed, shipped, arrived at the airport to ship, arrived in the states, and moved from facility to facility until it arrived at my house. The items were securely packaged together in a plastic covering, not in a box. However, they were not loosely flailing around. They were packaged well and there was no damage to the package even though it (according to the text updates) traveled through many facilities. The items were just as shown on the website. Products seem to be well made, true to color, and size. I am impressed and will likely order from this company again in the future as the prices are reasonable and the products of good quality.

title: Shopping like a socialite!
text:
Absolutely no complaints! I‚Äôve placed 24 orders so far and every transaction has gone smoothly. My husband downloaded the app and is hooked now too! 
It‚Äôs kinda like an online dollar store. Just be mindful of your purchases. Meaning - read descriptions thoroughly, read feedbacks thoroughly, especially PAY ATTENTION TO MEASUREMENTS! Can‚Äôt emphasize that one enough! Examples - my husband is an XL on American sizes but on Temu he needs to order XXL or XXXL. Also, most of their photos are enlarged so don‚Äôt judge something by the image but the measurements. If a listing doesn‚Äôt specify ‚Äúglass or plastic‚Äù then it‚Äôs most likely plastic. 
When I‚Äôve had a few items that weren‚Äôt exactly what I wanted or didn‚Äôt fit etc., Temu resolved my concerns promptly! 
Overall, it‚Äôs a fun app to shop with without breaking the bank. Especially if you‚Äôre into crafting, have small children or a really cheap husband üòâ

title: Getting harder to trust now
text:
I‚Äôve done nearly 30 orders over the last year. Suddenly they‚Äôre losing them. One package never left China, the other UPS decided to deliver miles away and it never showed up for me. Another also said delivered but they showed them dropping it off in some random bushes. 
Item quality is mixed, but I‚Äôve ordered a lot because you can find good things and they refund you easily if you dislike your items. 
But the reviews are often mixed on items. Meaning sometimes they‚Äôre all fluff, where it‚Äôs people saying the same thing over and over, or things that don‚Äôt make sense, they put ‚Äúmy grandson loves it!‚Äù on a lot of reviews. They copy keyterms that I put in my reviews and post it over and over to boost the sale of their items. It‚Äôs very weird. It worked for so long and now I‚Äôm getting mad that my items just don‚Äôt even show up. There‚Äôs no point in trying to order again and again if someone else is gonna always get my things for free or the items I carefully chose keep going sold out.

title: Great shopping app
text:
Let me tell you something right now. All the little games they have? The real way you get free stuff is by referring people, ignore all the flashy animations engineered to make you feel like youre winning at a lottery or something. The only way temu will give you free stuff is referring someone, and temu WANTS PROOF thats this person you referring is using the app. That‚Äôs the only way. Its marketing at the end of the day, if you came to this app for the free stuff, you will leave disappointed. This aspect seems more appropriate to influencers n such so they can give decent stuff to fuel their brand. 

Now on to shopping. They legit have good deals on homeware, kitchen stuff, and storage. OH MY GOD THE STORAGE OPTIONS! I don't care too much for the clothing since i use another app for that. But id say if youre looking for well made cheap stuff for the home, kitchen, bed, etc, youve come to the right place.

title: Shopping was fun and easy
text: I admit my expectations were low. You usually get what you pay for.  But I was really surprised at the quality of most of the items.  I bought two tshirts. The material was fantastic but didn‚Äôt really fit. I wear 3x and ordered 5x as suggested.  I could put them on but they were to tight for me. The material and workmanship were great and I was disappointed I couldn‚Äôt wear them.  Then I bought $190 worth of little gadgets, fun things, things to use at school etc.  I had coupons for $140 so I paid $59  and it was fun and enjoyable going thru the box. Out of all of it there was only one thing that didn‚Äôt work that was a suction cup thing to take dents out of your car.  I also bought one of the rompers. I loved it again size 5.  It fit but in me was tight in the wrong places. I gave it to my niece who wears 1x-2x and it looked great on her but a little long. So have fun.

title: You Get what you pay for.

For example the type of material the metal is and if it‚Äôs silver plated or chrome plated. Even the coins. Are these real or mass produced and made from what? I know you get what you pay for. Even though cheaply made in third world countries I may order again because I do like the look of many things listed and where else can you get something for that price that you like the looks of! Everything was packaged nicely and I was kept informed on my shipment! Thanks, Randy

title: Shipping, clothing and shoes
text:
To start most people don't realize that these items have to pass through customs.  That's where shipping gets delayed and becomes a waiting game.  This part is not actually Temu's fault.   Customs does things on their own schedule.  
If you buy clothing, buy a size up.  The clothing runs small.  Same with the shoes and the shoes all seem to be narrow fit.  HAND WASH all the clothing you buy and do NOT put it in a dryer even on the delicate cycle.  One trip in the washer and dryer and the thread that holds the clothes together falls out. Happily I can sew. But still the clothing doesn't last long even if you hand wash it.  Expect to only wear the clothing you buy from here a couple of times unless you want to re-sew everything. 
The household items are the same quality of what you buy in a dollar store.  But I'm not sure why anyone would expect anything different with the prices these items are.  
I will order little things here and there but not clothes or shoes again.

title: Disappointed
text: Don‚Äôt get me wrong this app is amazing. The products I‚Äôve ordered have all be amazing and great quality for low price! And I‚Äôve made several orders. How ever I don‚Äôt like how there are so many games and so many ways to win free gifts and things and yet they are all so impossible to win. I‚Äôve spent months on the app. And I‚Äôve learned each games time always seems to run out right when you‚Äôre about to win the free prizes. Maybe I just have bad luck. I‚Äôm not sure but it seems to never fail when I‚Äôm a few percentages away from growing the adult fish or a few bucks from the free gift or a few coins away from getting the last prize from the 3 hat trick game my time runs out and I have to start the game over. You‚Äôd think after purchasing so many items the games would become easier to win to keep costumers attention. Getting the free items would help boost sales. But as I said maybe I just have poor luck.

title: Good value and prices for many products particularly clothing.
text: I have ordered numerous items - including clothing and shoes for men and women and a number of gadgets.  The best have been the clothing items although the fabric has not always been good- particularly for the man‚Äôs shirt.  Also had to return one woman‚Äôs top as fabric was unsatisfactory although print colors were good.  The very  inexpensive items are the worst for value and quality.  It is not worth returning them- so I am absorbing one or two that totally did not work as loss leaders for the many others that were satisfactory or better in quality.    All in all, Temu provides good products for far less than the equivalent in the domestic market.  The free shipping policy is also a plus as are the incentives for buying more from them.  I have not looked into the allegations of their unfair labor practices which others have alleged.
